<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
Is an Elven cloak [4,+8] (+4) 's pval +4 the same as +4.000 Stealth skill is? <p>
I know that negative skills doesn't work yet, but would a rohanknight with a total of +8 stealth equipment be equal to 0 stealth? 
</p>
<p>
<a href="./MassimilianoMarangio">MassimilianoMarangio</a>: Items are not changed in the actual version. This means that the pval +4 is added to the internal Stealth ability (Stealth at skill level 50.0 adds only 25 points to the ability, i.e. the cloak is equivalent to 8 skill levels). A RohanKnight would need equipment with +8 to the Stealth ability or 16.0 skill levels in the Stealth skill to remove his penality. 
</p>
